BEGIN:VCALENDAR
VERSION:2.0
PRODID://Kansas City Bitcoiners//Events//EN
CALSCALE:GREGORIAN
METHOD:PUBLISH
X-WR-CALNAME:Kansas City Bitcoin Meetup Group
X-WR-CALDESC:<p>We're a group focused on all things Bitcoin. All experience levels welcome\, whether you're new and curious or have been in the scene for years.</p> \n<p>We meet regularly for casual discussions and presentations on topics like the protocol and software\, economics\, trading\, storage techniques\, investing\, and mining.</p> \n<p>Come out to meet\, learn from\, and share ideas with fellow Bitcoiners!</p> \n<p>Note that we are not a "blockchain" or "cryptocurrency" group. There are plenty of those around. We're Bitcoiners here to talk Bitcoin.</p>
X-WR-TIMEZONE:America/Chicago
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:311997123@kansas-city-bitcoin-meetup.com
DTSTART:20260205T003000Z
DTEND:20260205T023000Z
DTSTAMP:20260123T202248Z
CREATED:20251113T221813Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260123T202248Z
SUMMARY:Circular Economy Building
DESCRIPTION:Bitcoin is money\, let's use it as such!\nBring whatever wares you have for sale\, browse others\, and have a beer.\n\nEvent URL: https://www.meetup.com/kansas-city-bitcoin-meetup-group/events/311997123/
LOCATION:1725 McGee Street\, Kansas City\, MO
URL:https://www.meetup.com/kansas-city-bitcoin-meetup-group/events/311997123/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
