SUMMARY:Coffee with KC Bitcoiners!
DESCRIPTION:**Join us for KC Bitcoiners Coffee**\n\n🍩☕\nCome hang out\, grab a coffee\, and connect with fellow Bitcoiners. Bring your questions\, thoughts\, or the latest news. Whether you're new to Bitcoin or have been around since the early days\, you're welcome here.\n\n🚫 Just a reminder: we're not a "blockchain" or "crypto" group. We're here to talk Bitcoin.\n\nLook forward to seeing you there! Let us know if you have any questions.\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\nDONATE to support future KC Bitcoiners events:\n[https://btcpay0.voltageapp.io/apps/26q7Q6PpDTZFoUBfpMko6jSzm4od/pos](https://btcpay0.voltageapp.io/apps/26q7Q6PpDTZFoUBfpMko6jSzm4od/pos)\n\nEvent URL: https://www.meetup.com/kansas-city-bitcoin-meetup-group/events/311998847/
LOCATION:200 NE Chipman Rd\, Lee's Summit\, MO
URL:https://www.meetup.com/kansas-city-bitcoin-meetup-group/events/311998847/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
